Einstein Personalization

Einstein Personalization is a Customer 360 application that works with Data Cloud to provide personalized experiences across Salesforce clouds. Combining optimized key business objectives with rules-based targeting and decision making, Einstein Personalization delivers real-time, personalized decisions across channels.

Use Einstein Personalization to deliver timely, relevant, personalized experiences. As a new Customer 360 application built on Data Cloud, Einstein Personalization provides AI-based recommendations and personalized content to customers or site visitors in real time.
